claim.claim-text:
1. A three-part clasp for a pumping garment for hands-free pumping, the three-part clasp comprising:
a male part attached to a shoulder strap of the pumping garment;
a first female part attached to an inner layer of the pumping garment, the inner layer including an aperture for insertion of a breast pump flange;
a second female part attached to an outer layer of the pumping garment;
in a doubly fastened configuration, the first female part connected to the male part, the second female part connected to the male part, and the first female part and the second female part arranged side-by-side.

14. A three-part clasp for a pumping garment for hands-free pumping, the three-part clasp comprising:
a male part attached to a shoulder strap of the pumping garment;
a first female part attached to an inner layer of the pumping garment, the inner layer including an aperture for insertion of a breast pump flange;
a second female part attached to an outer layer of the pumping garment;
in a doubly fastened configuration, the first female part connected to the male part, the second female part connected to the male part, and the second female part configured to be stacked upon the first female part.
